seo: Spring Cloud Config,目录遍历漏洞,安全检测
seo_en: Spring Cloud Config,Directory Traversal Vulnerability,Security Testing
summary: 该插件用于检测Spring Cloud Config Server是否存在目录遍历漏洞，通过发送特定请求检查是否可以访问敏感文件。
summary_en: This plugin is used to detect whether the Spring Cloud Config Server has a directory traversal vulnerability by sending specific requests to check if access to sensitive files is possible.
